    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/c888e761a6b799378f722ffa2f1ca3ab.avif?t=1596614667\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.poster.avif?t=1596614667\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.webm?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.mp4?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Boss Defiance-Heroic Edition是一款街机/动作竞赛和非对称游戏，具有多人游戏和本地合作，最多可容纳4位玩家。<br><br>您可以选择成为一名强大的老板，或是与他作战的英勇英雄之一。<br>老板将在地牢中与其他玩家/角色对抗，直到另一个地牢，直到死亡。<br>为了成功，它需要到达地牢的尽头，杀死所有将以他的方式找到的英雄。<br>相反，英雄们需要合作以阻止邪恶的敌人到达竞技场的尽头，从而获胜。<br>游戏具有两种不同的模式：普通模式和野兽模式，其中Boss更加强大和危险！<br>两种模式最多可播放4位玩家。<br><br>在这个令人兴奋的动作沙发游戏中，重新发现与您的朋友并肩玩耍的乐趣，并度过了无数个小时的乐趣！<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/006896722ce3c817920ec9fe4d1da3fe.avif?t=1596614667\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.poster.avif?t=1596614667\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.webm?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.